Ctrl + K, Ctrl + O → Open Folder

Ctrl + Alt + Up/Down → Add Multi-Cursor

*Ctrl + Shift + * → Jump to Matching Bracket

Ctrl + M → Toggle Tab Moves Focus

Front-End Development Shortcuts

Ctrl + E, Ctrl + E → Emmet Expand Abbreviation

Ctrl + Shift + [ / ] → Fold/Unfold Code Blocks

Alt + Click → Add Multiple Cursors

Ctrl + Shift + I → Format Code (Prettier)

Ctrl + Shift + M → Show Errors and Warnings

Ctrl + Shift + U → Convert to Uppercase/Lowercase

Debugging & Live Preview

F12 → Go to Definition

Ctrl + Click → Peek Definition

Ctrl + Shift + V → Open Markdown Preview

Ctrl + Shift + P, then type Live Server: Open with Live Server → Start Live Server

Terminal & Git

Ctrl + ` → Toggle Integrated Terminal

Ctrl + Shift + C → Open New Terminal

Ctrl + Shift + G → Open Source Control (Git)

Ctrl + K + U → Stage All Changes

Ctrl + K + R → Discard Changes

